snippet.title: THE MULLER-POWELL PRINCIPLE | Announcement Trailer | Upcoming First-Person Sci-fi Adventure
snippet.description:
COMING IN 2023 TO PC AND CONSOLES

A sci-fi puzzle thriller taking place in the early 2030’s. You are Harry Herman, an employee of a science company Delta Laboratories that studies interdimensional traveling. You’ve been participating in a project that supposed to benefit all humanity, but something went wrong, and now you’re stuck far away from home. Make your way back to Earth, find clues, uncover mysterious connections between the worlds you visit and reveal the Delta Labs' ultimate dark secret...

Made by Three Dots using Unreal Engine

STEAM PAGE: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2155770/THE_MULLERPOWELL_PRINCIPLE/
OUR DISCORD: https://discord.gg/E2kPNzrd7G
